When implementing any new feature in AURAN:
1. Always create admin_settings seed data for any numeric/text/rate values
2. Always add admin UI controls in /super-console for those settings  
3. Always use getSetting('category','key') hook instead of hardcoded values
4. Never hardcode points, rates, conditions, or thresholds
5. Commit and push after every completed task

This rule applies to ALL features without exception.

